{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Terminate the Avanti West Coast Mainline contract",
        "additional_details": "According to figures released by the Office of Rail and Road in November 2022, Avanti West Coast had the worst record of train cancellations in the year prior to this date, with a cancellation rate of 8%. \r\n \r\nSince then, there has been little to suggest \"drastic\" improvement has occurred since the Government demanded this in October 2022. \r\n \r\nWe demand a better provider and so the contract should be terminated.\r\n",
        "background": "The Government should terminate the West Coast contract with Avanti and re-tender.\r\nSince the contract was awarded in 2019, Avanti have had a history of failure in running the service\r\n",
